Netwroking files are stored in cd /$ORACLE_HOME/network/admin
  in the bin we can create the listner using command:netmgr(UTILITY)

expand on local
expand on listeners
click + symbol which is in green color.

enter name of listener
listener
click on OK 
click on add address
in the host you can give hostname or ipaddress.

in the drop down above switch it from listening locations to database services.
click on add database.

Global db name : proddb
SID : proddb
file save network configuration
file exit.
